item.title: CVE-2022-4060|2024-08-03T01:27:54.404Z -- unknown -- user%20post%20gallery
item.description: The User Post Gallery WordPress plugin through 2.19 does not limit what callback functions can be called by users, making it possible to any visitors to run code on sites running it.
